author: JiwonYu
title: Park Myung Soo Reveals His Reading Habits In Effort To Surpass Yoo Jae Suk
text:
Pin   
During the January 2 broadcast of KBS CoolFM’s “ Park Myung Soo ’s Radio Show,” Park Myung Soo revealed his efforts to beat Yoo Jae Suk . 
Comedian Yoo Min Sang came as a guest this day, and they talked about how comedian Kim Joon Hyun’s popularity increased due to mukbangs (eating shows). Park Myung Soo asked, “Weren’t you jealous?” and Yoo Min Sang said, “Honestly, I’m still jealous.” 
Being the new year, Park Myung Soo comforted him, saying, “You’re as good as Joon Hyun.” Then Yoo Min Sang returned the compliment with, “I’m envious of the relationship you have with Yoo Jae Suk. I like your kind of character.” 
Then Park Myung Soo told him, “I read five books when I’m at home in an effort to beat Jae Suk. I recently read ‘Who Moved My Cheese’ and ‘Your Best Life Now.’ I’m reading old books again these days.”
